## Description {#details}

This class represents an item in the work list.

The type defines what kind of work needs to be performed when processing the current item. The flags and info fields are optional based on the type.

Definition at line 356 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/dwarflinker/include/llvm/dwarflinker/classic/dwarflinker-h">DWARFLinker.h</a>.
